Name: Froggy
About the game: 'Froggy' is a gem collecting puzzle game about little (but smart) frog who is going to beat through many unique levels. It's a nice one for all puzzle lovers! Game Features: Play as a handsome froggy Collect beautiful gemstones to unlock portals Build tiles to build your own way Beat 20 unique, hand made levels Steam Achievements support Some levels are very difficult - use your brain! Simple but cute pixelart style We hope this game will be a real challenge for everyone who dares to try!
